text: Good park, although small but the slide and playground is nice and clean. Feels quite new also. The tree and vegetation also decent and give good protection from heat. A bit hiding and no toilet.

Quiet. Safe. And clean.
Lots of families and little kids past 5pm.
I wish they had toilet facilities too so if you need to go during workouts, you have that option.

Quiet weekday afternoon, lying on the deck, looking up at the rain tree, the light from the clouds emanating and streaming through the gaps in the leaves. The cool breeze lures me into an afternoon slumber. Life seems to slow.
Small but interesting. There's a round swig that u can lie down. Suitable for a family after meal walk.

Excellent revamp to the dull playground previously. Never seen so many neighbors before! Suitable for 3yo and up with parental supervision of course. Jungle theme. My kids just love coming back for a challenge.
